{"tid":1849580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「賊性難改」強國呃日資公司提供100萬個口罩","createTime":"2020-01-29T06:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T06:45:08.000Z","uid":131548,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ada29e929288a5b9c2d77305800c62c4c6eca24","tid":1849580,"uid":131548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"//中國政府主動要求<br />\n伊藤洋華堂提供100萬個口罩給中國<br />\n同時發動網絡輿論攻勢造成是伊藤洋華堂&ldquo;免費贈送&rdquo;<br />\n要脅伊藤洋華堂免費供應捐贈口罩<br />\n伊藤洋華堂表示從來沒有提過免費贈送的事情<br />\n接到要求時以爲中方是真金白銀購買<br />\n因爲情勢緊急日方寬鬆處理先到貨後付款<br />\n誰知到貨後中方突然變臉稱到貨爲贈品<br />\n伊藤洋華堂現在是相當尷尬<br />\n只能先承諾無論如何會盡力協助災區受害者<br />\n真是厲害了強國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPkhCmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPkhCmS.jpg&h=1c57b855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://article.yahoo.co.jp/detail/dc09199ce074e19bd4d8b20a1fccfc6f841b55e6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farticle.yahoo.co.jp%2Fdetail%2Fdc09199ce074e19bd4d8b20a1fccfc6f841b55e6&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=24ab4ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://article.yahoo.co.jp/detail/dc09199ce074e19bd4d8b20a1fccfc6f841b55e6</a><br />\n<br />\nFb:日堯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/653010246/posts/10163124352695247/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F653010246%2Fposts%2F10163124352695247%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=bb311254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/653010246/posts/10163124352695247/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d110dd7327fab5878e392a34daef69923d35d0ee","tid":1849580,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"呃人錢， 100 萬個，每個賣5 蚊咁好和味賺500萬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港所有口岸封鎖所有大陸護照人士進入，直至疫症停止。<br />\n<br />\n入黎投個票支持下<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/t?id=1053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.o